# Review-engine reports/verdicts are LOCAL working artifacts — the PR body is the audit trail
# (see ../README.md; matrices are the durable record, code-reviews are not). Ignore them so a
# clean autorun/build exit never leaves untracked review litter in the operator's repo. The
# operator can still read the latest report on disk; it just isn't committed.
*
!.gitkeep
!.gitignore
